    <title>Sincerely Stefanie: Employees Should Stay Home When Sick </title>
    <link>http://ehstoday.com/health/sincerely-stefanie-employees-should-stay-home-when-sick</link>
    <description>

    &lt;div class=&quot;field-deck&quot;&gt;

        
        
                
                Even when you think you aren&#039;t contagious, you might still be. 
                
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;node-body article-body&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;I had an eventful holiday season. I went to three different houses, visited my family and watched as many of them came down with the stomach flu.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The issue began with my niece two days before Christmas Eve. Usually bubbly and charismatic, she was confined to her bed. Sparing the details, my mother took care of her, cleaning up the mess and making sure she had plenty of fluids.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


